Revision history for dezi-client-php

0.001000  10 Oct 2011
    * initial release

0.001001  24 Oct 2011
    * fix tests to conform with Dezi server >= 0.1.5
    * set user agent on internal Pest object

0.001002  3 Sept 2012
    * support Dezi 0.001008 with commit() and rollback()

0.002000  12 Sept 2012
    * support Dezi 0.002000 with username/password basic auth

0.002001  14 Oct 2012
    * add server_supports_transactions()

0.002002  15 Oct 2012
    * set mtime in request header when indexing

0.002003  17 Oct 2012
    * add Dezi_Response->suggestions for Dezi 0.002004

1.1.1  14 Aug 2015
    * Convert to proper composer package
    * Uses proper composer naming scheme, now 1.1.1
